data.description: Perfect for first-time home buyers or for those who are down-sizing! This all brick ranch home is full of character and updates!  Extremely well-maintained, providing the convenience of one-level living, offering ease in commuting, and situated close to many amenities. Updated spacious kitchen, new furnace and water heater, extra finished living space in the basement with a half bath and separate office/gym/flex room. The back deck overlooks a generous fully fenced backyard. Make an offer today! Seller is motivated! Please note, missing fence pieces are on-site, however, seller has been unable to re-install due to weather.
